= !GeneBank =

The *!GeneBank* module is base on the [http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genbank GeneBank] data source. The next figure shows the relational schema for the *GeneBank* module. This module can handled any database using the [http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/Sitemap/samplerecord.html GeneBank] file format
